The RTC module uses I2C2 and needs to be set up a follows:\par
OPTION SYSTEM I2C GP22, GP15\par
\par
The micro SD card needs to be set up as follows:\par
OPTION SDCARD GP13, GP11, GP12, GP10\par
\par
Audio is initialised as:\par
OPTION AUDIO GP6, GP7\par
